{"tid":193901,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一念無明連阿東D藥呢幕都做得咁真實","createTime":"2017-04-09T15:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T17:06:49.000Z","uid":79353,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4cbd1c2b81543e95f662d9b06a580ef9982d2ef","tid":193901,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"戲入面阿東唔肯食藥，將D藥嘔晒出黎：<br />\n紫色果粒藥叫epilim，現實中真係醫bipolar<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FLXpW9U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFLXpW9U.jpg&h=0da1bc26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我曾經食過同一隻藥：(不過已自行停藥)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WQtBs18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWQtBs18.jpg&h=de8a77e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就冇bipolar<br />\n<br />\n不過上年醫畜話癲癇都有機會導致某些症狀<br />\n<br />\n所以捉左朕去照腦電圖<br />\n<br />\n然後結果顯示腦電波有問題，接近癲癇發作<br />\n<br />\n佢怕我真係會發作所以開epilim預防下..."},{"pid":"dada848a7cabf028273d6b22bdc8f85b83834f48","tid":193901,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:16:04.000Z","msg":"有冇人認到另外三隻藥係咩藥???"},{"pid":"5297da9a5312e203f96025f79b27978127ccbac0","tid":193901,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本野黎姐下話。。。"},{"pid":"194df7a2b5427f7bd16662cfb00c0d428bca96ca","tid":193901,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本野黎姐下話。。。</blockquote><br />\n好難講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633931c5357bed35f5391785a8cd106e3956cda3","tid":193901,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T15:18:18.000Z","msg":"得朕呢個無聊人先會將youtube段片重播左五次<br />\n<br />\n為左CAP低呢一幕 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\